~ start
Makoto: [[Hi|Hello|Howdy]], this is some dialogue. [#expression_left=neutral][#actor_right=off]
Makoto: What should I get from don don rice? [#expression_left=confused]
[wait=1]
- First one
	Makoto: You picked the first one. [#expression_left=happy]
- Second one
	Makoto: You picked the second one. [#expression_left=angry]
- Start again => start
- End the conversation => END
Makoto: For more information see the online documentation. [#expression_left=unimp]
=> END

~ start2
Makoto: badabing badaboom this is what i call [outline_size=8][color=gold][wave amp=10.0 freq=5.0 connected=1]camera zoom[/wave][/color][/outline_size] [#expression_left=happy][#camera_animation=zoom_in][#actor_right=off]
Makoto: okay this is jank asf i gotta fix shit [#expression_left=unimp]
Makoto: lets get outta here [#camera_animation=zoom_out]
do Global.prepareDialogue("testFlag")
do Global.testThing()
=> END

~ start3
Makoto: who the hell is this guy [#expression_left=unimp][#animate_left=enter_convo][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=yumi]
Makoto: you look like a mean fella
John: im john yo [#animate_left=exit_convo][#animate_right=enter_convo]
John: nice to meet u im actually really nice[#expression_right=happy]
Makoto: oh okay :) [#expression_left=neutral][#animate_left=enter_convo][#animate_right=exit_convo]
Ina: hello my name is Ina please don't end the convo-- [#animate_left=exit_convo][#expression_right=happy][#animate_right=enter_convo][#new_actor=ina]
=> END	

~ dinoObtained
Makoto: Oh boy! A Dino Nugget! [#expression_left=happy]
	
~ functionTest
Ina: this is for testing other functions [#animate_left=exit_convo][#expression_right=happy][#animate_right=enter_convo][#actor_right=on][#new_actor=ina]
Ina: Can you get me a figurine from the toy store?
do Global.searchInv("fox_toy")
if Global.playerHasItem == false
	=> END
elif Global.playerHasItem == true
	Ina: Oh wow, I've been waiting for this one! :3
	=> END
	
~ oneShotTest
